snippet.title: REDO! - Release Date Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
REDO!, a dark, evocative non-linear action RPG, is coming to Nintendo Switch on June 22, 2022.

The age of humanity has gone. In a world dominated by biomachines, monstrosities, dolls and the cold - a voice beckons you out into the ruins - “Meet me at the Solar Cathedral.”

#REDO #NintendoSwitch
